      <title>卡特中心将派团队观察委内瑞拉选举</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-19/carter-center-to-send-a-team-to-observe-venezuelan-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于欧盟观察员被排除在外，引发了人们对委内瑞拉选举过程合法性的担忧，卡特中心将派遣一个小组观察委内瑞拉下个月的选举。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-19/carter-center-to-send-a-team-to-observe-venezuelan-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Jun 2024 21:28:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
